  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a non-stick pan over medium heat.",
    "Add garlic and chili peppers (if using) to sauté for about 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Fold in smoked muffin pieces, green onions, soy sauce, and lemon juice. Stir well to combine.",
    "Pour water into the pan and bring to a simmer.",
    "Simmer the mixture for about 5 minutes or until the liquid has reduced by half.",
    "Turn off heat and let it sit for another minute before serving."
